                                "editor": "<p>When ready to serve, bring a large saucepan of salted water to the boil. Heat the tomato and basil sauce until simmering. Drop the gnocchi into the boiling water and, when they rise to the surface, scoop out and toss through the warmed tomato sauce, then transfer to a large warm serving bowl.<\/p>",
